<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>You’ve Reached Your Limit for Free Published Simulations</title>
</head>
<style>
    * {
        font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;

        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            body {
                background-color: #f9fafb;
            }

            main {
                box-shadow: 0px 1px 3px 0px #0000000d;
            }

            .container {
                display: grid;
                place-items: center;
            }
        }
    }
</style>

<body>
    <div class="container" style="display: grid; height: 100vh">
        <main style="
          max-width: 528px;
          width: Fixed (528px) px;
          height: Hug (806px) px;
          padding: 40px 24px 24px 24px;
          gap: 40px;
          border-radius: 8px 0px 0px 0px;
          opacity: 0px;
          background-color: #fff;
        ">
            <img style="height: 40px; object-fit: contain; margin-bottom: 40px" src="{{{logoUrl}}}" />

            <div>
                <h1 style="font-size: 20px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 40px">
                    You’ve Reached Your Limit for Free Published Simulations
                </h1>

                <div>
                    <p style="
              font-size: 16px;
              font-weight: 500;
              line-height: 24.8px;
              text-align: left;
              text-underline-position: from-font;
              color: #727679;
              text-decoration-skip-ink: none;
            ">
                        Dear {{recipient}},
                    </p>

                    <p style="
              font-size: 16px;
              font-weight: 500;
              line-height: 24.8px;
              text-align: left;
              text-underline-position: from-font;
              color: #727679;
              text-decoration-skip-ink: none;
            ">
                        You’ve successfully published 3 simulations as part of your free
                        account, and while you’ve reached your limit for free public
                        published services, don’t worry!
                    </p>

                    <p style="
              font-size: 16px;
              font-weight: 500;
              line-height: 24.8px;
              text-align: left;
              text-underline-position: from-font;
              color: #727679;
              text-decoration-skip-ink: none;
            ">
                        You can still create and work on unlimited drafts to develop more
                        simulations.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div style="margin-bottom: 40px">
                    <p style="
              font-size: 16px;
              font-weight: 500;
              line-height: 24.8px;
              text-align: left;
              text-underline-position: from-font;
              color: #727679;
              text-decoration-skip-ink: none;
            ">
                        Thank you for being a valued part of Nudgyt! We can’t wait to see
                        your next simulation.
                    </p>
                    <br />
                    <p style="
              font-size: 16px;
              font-weight: 500;
              line-height: 24.8px;
              text-align: left;
              text-underline-position: from-font;
              color: #727679;
              text-decoration-skip-ink: none;
            ">
                        Best regards,
                        <br />
                        <br />
                        The [Platform Name] Team
                    </p>
                </div>
                <hr style="margin-bottom: 40px" />
                <div>
                    <img src="{{{logoUrl}}}" style="height: 20px; object-fit: contain" />
                    <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #727679">
                        © 2025 Nudgyt Pte. Ltd. <br />
                        Singapore
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </main>
    </div>
</body>

</html>